  <acronym>STRIVE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Long-term, Multi-center, Longitudinal Post-marketing, Observational Study to Assess Long Term Safety and Effectiveness of HUMIRA® (Adalimumab) in Children With Moderately to Severely Active Polyarticular or Polyarticular-course Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis (JIA) - STRIVE</official_title>
